Blessing "Yemi" Mobolade (amụrụ n'afọ 1978 ma ọ bụ n'afọ 1979) bụ onye ọchụnta ego na onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị Naijiria-Amerịka. Ọ bụ onye isi obodo nke 42 nke Colorado Springs, Colorado, a ṅụrụ iyi na June 6, 2023.
A mụrụ Mobolade ma zụlite ya na Lagos, Naịjirịa. Nna Mobolade rụrụ ọrụ na ego maka exoon Mobil mgbe nne ya bụ onye nkuzi ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị
O nwere nwanne nwoke tọrọ ya na ụmụnne nwanyị abụọ ọ tọrọ. N'ọnwa Ọgọstụ afọ 1996, Mobolade kwagara na United States
Ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Mahadum betheln'afọ 2001. O nwetara nzere masta na Mahadum Indiana Wesleyan na njikwa na idu ndú na Master of Divinity na A.W
Tozer Theological Seminary na mahadin Samson.

In 2010, Mobolade settled in Coloraso spring Colorado He co-founded two restaurants, founded a church within the christain missionary alliance and was a ministry leader at the First Presbyterian Church of Colorado Springs between 2015 and 2017. Mobolade was the vice president of business retention for Colorado Springs' chamber of commercefrom 2017 to 2019 and small business development manager for Colorado Springs from 2019 to 2022.

Mobolade kwupụtara na ọ ga-abụ onye isi obodo Colorado Springs na ntuli aka 2023 dị ka onye ndọrọ ndoro ọchịchị nwere onwe ya n'ọnwa Eprel 2022. Na ntuli aka na-abụghị nke ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị, nke e mere na Eprel 4, Mobolade mechara bụrụ onye mbụ na mpaghara 12 na pasent 29 nke votu, na-aga n'ihu na ntuli nke abuomegide onye Republican Wayne W

Williams, onye bụbu odeakwụkwọ nke steeti, onye nwetara pasent 20. Mobolade meriri Williams na ntuli aka nke abụọ na Mee 16, pasent 57 ruo pasent 43, iji bụrụ onye isi ojii mbụ a họpụtara dịka onye isi obodo Colorado Springs na onye isi obodo mbụ a họọrọ nke na-abụghị onye otu Republican Party. A ṅụrụ ya iyi n'ọkwa na June 6.
Mobolade ghọrọ nwa amaala United States na 2017
Ọ zutere nwunye ya, Abbey, na Indiana; ha nwere ụmụ atọ.
